  "text": "The Cartan forms that arise in the non-linear realisation E 11 ⊗ s l 1 in five dimensions can be found in [CITATION_1] . This paper derived all the gauged supergravities in five dimensions by taking the fields to have a non-trivial dependence on the generalised space-time.",
